data.description: PEACEFUL AND PRIVATE!  3BR, 2.5 BTH, 3,466 total sqft with 3 car garage on 5.2 acres. INCLUDES, 830 sqft caretaker unit with separate entry. Main level features radiant floor heating, laminate, tile and carpet flooring, granite tile kitchen counters, stainless appliances. Great Mt. Sopris views from living area, dining area and deck with some selective tree trimming!  Large master bedroom with walk-in closet. 314 sqft unfinished basement for media or exercise room or ??  Low maintenance exterior is mostly brick and some aluminum siding, soffit and fascia and metal roof.  Lock-off caretaker unit features radiant floor heating, kitchenette and full bath.  Property has radon mitigation system and is set up for generator back-up power.  Cell phone will require booster or WI-FI.
